1 Data set の用意　womenraw.xls からdataframe をつくる

  • CARME-N.org には、xlsでファイルが用意されている
.d <- read_excel(path="womenraw.xls")

.d %>% mutate(Q1 = factor(Q1),Q2 = factor(Q2),Q3 = factor(Q3),Q4 = factor(Q4),
              C = factor(C),G= factor(G),A=factor(A),M=factor(M),E=factor(E)) -> .d.f

name_tbl_Q <- setNames(c("W","w","H","?"),1:4)
name_tbl_C <- setNames(c("AUS","DW","DE","GB","NIRL","USA","A","H","I","IRL","NL","N","S","CZ",
                          "SLO","PL","BG","RUS","NZ","CDN","RP","IL","J","E"),1:24)

name_tbl_G <- setNames(c("m","f"),1:2)
name_tbl_A <- setNames(c("<25","26-35","36-45","46-55","56-65",">66"),1:6)
name_tbl_M <- setNames(c("ma","wi","di","se","si",NA),c(1:5,9))
name_tbl_E <- setNames(c(NA,"E1","E2","E3","E4","E5","E6","E7","DK",NA),c(0:7,98,99))


.d.f %>% mutate(Q1 = recode(Q1,!!!name_tbl_Q),Q2 = recode(Q2,!!!name_tbl_Q),
                Q3 = recode(Q3,!!!name_tbl_Q),Q4 = recode(Q4,!!!name_tbl_Q),
                C = recode(C,!!!name_tbl_C),# 国
                G = recode(G,!!!name_tbl_G),# 性別
                A = recode(A,!!!name_tbl_A),# 年齢
                M = recode(M,!!!name_tbl_M),# 婚姻状態　-- 17章で使う
                E = recode(E,!!!name_tbl_E) # 学歴　　　-- 17章で使う
                ) -> .d.conv

#.d.conv %>% nrow()
.d.conv %>% summary()

6.1 Burt to FactoMineR::CA

res.CA.Burt <- CA(.d.Burt,graph = FALSE)
fviz_ca_biplot(res.CA.Burt,invisible = "row",repel = TRUE) + ylim(-2,3) + xlim(-1,3) +
  coord_fixed(ratio = 1)

.d.DWE %>% as.matrix() %>% burt() -> .d.DWE.sup.Burt
res.Burt.sup.CA <- CA(.d.DWE.sup.Burt,col.sup = 17:38,row.sup = 17:38,graph = FALSE)
fviz_ca_biplot(res.Burt.sup.CA,invisible = c("row","col"),repel = TRUE) + 
  xlim(-0.5,0.5) + ylim(-0.5,0.5) + coord_fixed(ratio = 1)
